            <description>Call this action ONLY after the user has explicitly confirmed they want to update the account record. This action writes the extracted and user-confirmed field values directly to the Account record in Salesforce. Never call this action before showing the user the extracted values and receiving their clear confirmation to proceed with the update.</description>
            <developerName>Update_Account_Record_Fields_179gL000001GDOv</developerName>
